&lt;p&gt;# Comments: 1&lt;/p&gt;</description><guid isPermaLink="false">https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=48065714</guid><pubDate>Fri, 08 May 2026 16:54:14 +0000</pubDate></item><item><title>Seeking small angel/co-founder for 7-year solo deterministic AI runtime project</title><link>https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=48065691</link><description>&lt;p&gt;After 7+ years of solo, self-funded research, I built a deterministic Linguistic Runtime — a fundamental solution to the modeling problem in AI.It is about creating and manipulating  reality models directly from natural language without LLM.&lt;p&gt;Grok (the least sycophantic AI) audit scores:&lt;p&gt;• Logical Soundness and Consistency: 9.7/10
• Demonstration: 9.3/10
• Roadmap: 9.3/10&lt;p&gt;Demo (proof of the modeling solution):&lt;p&gt;Sign-in → Inventory item addition → Order creation → Total/tax calculation with dynamic rules. All via pure natural language. No LLMs. No coding/code generation. No predefined classes/schemas/templates. No back-end or front-end APIs. Natural language is the API.&lt;p&gt;https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Y1I04_T5-RWTQzS1HngCzW5vIaeS7q4W/view?usp=drive_link&lt;p&gt;Sovereign Shell (Phase 1) is the first commercial product: a practical utility that turns natural language intent into reliable system commands for sysadmins and DevOps engineers. It is the most capital-efficient first step and will create a hardened codebase and industrial proof for future phases.&lt;p&gt;Roadmap (single codebase):
Phase 1: Sovereign Shell (current focus)
Phase 2: Software Builder — AI acts directly as software with dynamic UI
Phase 3: Domain-specific chatbots with real understanding and psychology
Phase 4: Hardware/edge integration
I am now looking for a small angel investment or co-founder help to incorporate the company and ship Phase 1 in the coming months.&lt;p&gt;Full Grok audit report: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1IDIyh5MMQTXa5ccWNmbRiGXone_8-dC1/view?usp=sharing&lt;p&gt;Demo + thesis:
 https://theantagonistai.substack.com/&lt;p&gt;I can share a detailed pitch deck with serious interested parties.Any genuine interest, advice, feedback,introductions orguidance would be greatly appreciated.&lt;/p&gt;
